comments: Dunn (CHI) makes marginal body contact with Beal (WAS) after his gather.
Parker (WAS) makes marginal contact with Markkanen's (CHI) front at the start of his drive.
Portis (CHI) makes incidental contact with Lopez's (CHI) right arm that does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact with Parker (WAS) in transition that does not affect his SQBR.
LAR shows Arcidiacono (CHI) makes slight contact with Parker's (WAS) arm/side after his gather, but it is marginal and Parker is able to move through it to complete the play.
Parker (WAS) and Markkanen (CHI) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
LAR and RAR show Satoransky (WAS) jumps slightly into Markkanen's (CHI) body after his gather, but contact is marginal and does not affect his ability to complete the play.
Satoransky (WAS) slightly extends his off-arm against Harrison's (CHI) front after crossing halfcourt, but the contact is marginal and does not affect Harrison's ability to defend.
Portis (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Dunn's (CHI) path and allows him to disengage.
Dunn (CHI) makes some contact with Beal's (WAS) right arm, but it is marginal and does not affect his SQBR or ability to pass.
Brown Jr. (WAS) hops consecutively on the same foot upon gathering the ball.
Markkanen (CHI) slightly extends his hands against Satoransky's (WAS) back upon disengaging from the pick
All flagrant fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Parker (WAS) and Markanen (CHI) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
[Observable in enhanced video] Beal (WAS) straddles the lane line for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
[Observable in enhanced video] Portis (WAS) steps out of bounds along the sideline at the start of his dribble.
Markanen (CHI) makes some contact with Parker's (WAS) right arm during rebounding, but it is marginal and does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Satoransky (WAS) commits a take foul on Arcidiacono (CHI).
As he rolls to the lane, Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact with his left hand to Dunn's (CHI) front that does not affect his ability to defend.
RAR shows Arcidiacono (CHI) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) left thigh as he is airborne during the jump shot attempt.
Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact with Lopez (CHI) that does not affect his SQBR during the drive.
Portis (WAS) rests his hands on Lopez' (CHI) midsection and makes marginal contact that does not affect his FOM.
Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact with Lopez (CHI) on the play; the whistled illegal contact is initiated by Satoransky (WAS), who dislodges Lopez from position after he receives the pass.
Dunn (CHI) and Beal (WAS) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
[Observable in enhanced video] Dunn (CHI) receives the pass and takes more than two steps after his gather.
Beal (WAS) briefly has his arms around Lopez's (CHI) midsection before correcting.
Lopez (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and does not deliver the contact.
Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact with Arcidiacono's (CHI) front that does not affect his ability to pass.
Parker (WAS) cleanly intercepts the pass intended for Lopez (CHI).
Dunn (CHI) commits the take foul on Beal (WAS).
Parker (WAS) rests his hand against Markkanen's (CHI) front and makes marginal contact that does not affect his FOM.
Beal (WAS) briefly has his arms around Lopez's (CHI) upper half before correcting.
Lopez (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Beal's (WAS) path and does not deliver the contact.
LAR shows Parker (WAS) makes marginal contact with Markkanen's (CHI) front that does not affect his ability to pass.
LLB shows Beal (WAS) reaches in and cleanly strips Dunn (CHI) of the ball during the drive.
[Observable in enhanced video] Upon gathering the loose ball, Dunn (CHI) moves his pivot foot.
LLB shows Beal (WAS) makes contact with Dunn's (CHI) left shoulder after making initial contact with the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Portis (WAS) makes incidental contact with Lopez's (CHI) body as he attempts to box him out during the rebound.

Harrison (CHI) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) front during the drive. There is not clear and conclusive video evidence determining whether or not Arcidiacono (CHI) makes contact with Beal's (WAS) right arm.
Beal (WAS) steps out of bounds along the baseline during his dribble.
LLB shows Harrison (CHI) makes contact with Beal's (WAS) right wrist during his jump shot attempt.
RAR shows Lopez (CHI) continues moving into Parker's (WAS) path and delivers leg to leg contact that affects his ability to defend.
Markkanen (CHI) and Portis (WAS) engage with each other without affecting the other's FOM.

RAR and RLS show Harrison (CHI) cleanly dislodges Parker (WAS) of the ball after his gather; however, Markkanen (CHI) makes contact with Parker's arm after his gather and affects his shot attempt before the ball is dislodged.
Beal (WAS) and Dunn (CHI) engage and disengage off ball without affecting the other's FOM.
Parker (WAS) crosses the plane of the free throw line before the ball has an opportunity to make contact with the rim.
Satoransky (WAS) commits the take foul on Dunn (CHI).
LLS and LLB show Harrison (CHI) makes clean contact with the ball during Beal's (WAS) upward shooting motion.
Correctly called backcourt violation.
Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact with Harrison (CHI) along the sideline that does not affect his ability to pass.
